{
"@context": [
"http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl.jsonld",
{
"ex": "https://hospital-example.org/",
"dbo": "http://dbpedia.org/ontology/",
"vcard": "http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#",
"ex:patientAge": { "@type": "xsd:integer" },
"ex:resourcePatientId": { "@type": "@id" },
"ex:subjectWardList": { "@type": "@id" }
}
],
"@type": "odrl:Set",
"uid": "ex:policy/P14",
"permission": [{
"@type": "odrl:Permission",
"assigner": {
"@type": ["odrl:Party", "dbo:Hospital"],
"uid": "ex:authority",
"vcard:fn": "Hospital"
},
"assignee": {
"@type": ["odrl:PartyCollection", "vcard:Group", "dbo:Person"],
"uid": "ex:groups/family",
"vcard:fn": "Legal Guardian"
},
"action": "odrl:read",
"target": "ex:systems/db/tables/Historial_Clinico",
"constraint": [{
"@type": "odrl:LogicalConstraint",
"and": [
{
"@type": "odrl:Constraint",
"leftOperand": "ex:patientAge",
"operator": "odrl:lt",
"rightOperand": 18
},
41
{
"@type": "odrl:Constraint",
"leftOperand": "ex:resourcePatientId",
"operator": "odrl:isPartOf",
"rightOperand": "ex:subjectWardList"
}
]
}]
}]
}
DesignObservation(Improvement):Currently,itisassumedthatex:subjectWardList
contains the pre-calculated list of the user’s wards. A more robust implementation
would require a dynamic subquery verifying the guardianship relationship in real-time
to prevent a guardian from accessing minors not under their specific care.
